# Related Projects (outside this workspace)

This workspace (`~/MindsetForge`) is the **Flutter app only** (`app.mindsetforge.app`). It does not
contain the marketing website — don't search here for hero sections, landing page copy, or
marketing components; go straight to the sibling repo below instead.

| What | Where | Stack |
|------|-------|-------|
| Marketing website (`mindsetforge.app`) | `~/mindsetforge-web` | Next.js, static export |
| Flutter app (`app.mindsetforge.app`, this repo) | `~/MindsetForge` | Flutter |

Full hosting/deploy details (sites, Firebase project, deploy commands, custom domain setup) are in
[deployment.md](/Users/jonathanbrannen/MindsetForge/deployment.md).

Deploy the marketing site with:

```bash
cd ~/mindsetforge-web && npm run deploy
```

If the user says "marketing site", "marketing website", "landing page", or "mindsetforge.app"
(without the `app.` prefix), they almost always mean `~/mindsetforge-web`, not this repo.
